olor: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28aa742b93cf7d986b206d3a13456697cbcfcee3","tid":1543401,"uid":198175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"咁你可以9叫遊花園嘛.<br />\n<br />\n早排台仔選舉玩票站調查, 電話民調, 好多都係9叫支持韓流, 搞到大台D大民調全部都錯晒, 破壞對方玩做勢配票."},{"pid":"d98131d9250bbfab8c731859f5229dc44b6f0141","tid":1543401,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"全 部人 去太子站，荔枝角站 送花 英文文宣 哭喪<br />\n不圍警署"},{"pid":"fab825f75309190e027cf11ee65873839cb7d367","tid":1543401,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28aa742b93cf7d986b206d3a13456697cbcfcee3","tid":1543401,"uid":198175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"咁你可以9叫遊花園嘛.<br />\n<br />\n早排台仔選舉玩票站調查, 電話民調, 好多都係9叫支持韓流, 搞到大台D大民調全部都錯晒, 破壞對方玩做勢配票."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:50:16.000Z","msg":"佢係人口調查可能"},{"pid":"033dabcad0f59541ca3352228198dea012a33b00","tid":1543401,"uid":72173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"搞啲辛苦落街既卒仔為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986621c7ac5b80bcf9bbed60eb89fa9421fd940c","tid":1543401,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"033dabcad0f59541ca3352228198dea012a33b00","tid":1543401,"uid":72173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"搞啲辛苦落街既卒仔為乜<img src=\"/as